reviewText: Item arrived on time and was as described.
I loved CatDog when I was little, now I am 15 years old (will turn 16 in February) and I am glad I have this to my movie collection.  I still love CatDog, Thanks amazon!!

Catdog needs to be released on DVD sometime soon, in 2009 perhaps. Old School Nichelodeon fans want shows like Catdog to add to their DVD Collection. Please Catdog on DVD in 2009 or 2010! At least take a break from SpongeBob SquarePants and put Catdog on DVD Release Schedule! Please again, release Catdog in the next few years!
CatDog is so much fun; too bad not on DVD, but that's OK. Very pleased.
